    "body": "I think the root cause it really the peer count, I was using `v1.3.0` for a while now and had a lot of issues with missing attestations. I am not sure if it should be able to submit attestations if the peer count is close to or completely 0. For me the peer count issue seems to be fixed in `v1.1.1` and it did not miss a single attestations for 2 days now.\r\n\r\nIn comparison this is how the peer count metrics look\r\n\r\n\r\n**v1.3.0**\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/38436224/214247274-c766a073-c486-4b38-a4fe-0ee2069fb610.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n**v1.1.1**\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/38436224/214247581-6c12f05a-2048-499e-9fd0-9f7f1d6323a9.png)\r\n\r\n",
